# The shell for bandit26 is not /bin/bash
# In bandit25 there is a sshkey for bandit26
#

The shell logs out immidiatly after displaying BANDIT26 text.

use:
cat /etc/passwd | grep bandit26
(...) /usr/bin/showtext

cat /usr/bin/showtext
(...)
more ~/text.txt
exit 0

note: Abuse the more command to trigger (making the terminal window very small!)

press `v` to enter vim
type :e /etc/bandit_pass/bandit26

